io.requery

Annotation Type Key


  • @Documented
 @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Key
    Indicates a field as being the primary key for the object. There can be more than one key per object, if multiple keys are defined they define the composite key for the table. Example: 
    
      @Entity
     public class AbstractPerson {
          @Key int id; // primary key
         ...
     }
